# ATM System

An ATM system with UI console. It's built with C#, MySQL, and layered architecture principles.

## Features

- Customer login
- Deposit money
- Withdraw money
- Check balance
- Admin account management
- MySQL database support
- Unit testing with xUnit and Moq
- GitHub Actions CI workflow

## Project Structure

- Models → account data
- Repositories → database operations
- Services → business logic
- UI → console menus and interaction

## Technologies

- C#
- .NET 10
- MySQL
- xUnit
- Moq
- GitHub Actions

## Database Setup

Import the included SQL file:

```sql
SOURCE atm_system.sql;
```

Database name: atm_system

## Run the Project

```bash
dotnet build
dotnet run --project ATMSystem
```

## Run Tests

```bash
dotnet test
```

## Coverage

Coverage reports can be generated with:

```bash
dotnet test --collect:"XPlat Code Coverage"
```

The service layer is fully unit tested at 100% coverage.

## CI/CD

GitHub Actions automatically builds and tests the project on every push.